HISTORY
=======

Release 0.1
-----------
	First release 2012/06/25
    svn revision : 298

Release 0.2
-----------

Release 0.3
-----------
    Correcting bug affecting linux users

Release 0.4
-----------
    undump command
    create corpus

  New :
    size(subcorpus) -> nmatch(subcorpus)
    size(corpus) -> N(corpus);
    size() is suppressed
    new function: N(subcorpus)

	ntype -> ntypes
	nvalue -> nvalues 
	ntoken -> ntokens
	nregion -> nregions

	cqi_dump_subcorpus now return NULL if the subcorpus contains no match (rather than crashing).

	corpus[[attribute]] is no more allowed; use corpus$attribute

	"[" operator for easily retreiving vector (or list of vectors) of tokens from the corpus.

	as.data.frame() for corpus and subcorpus
	as.list() for corpus and subcorpus

Release 0.5
-----------
	Created vignettes/ dir as required by new R standards
	Added cleanup script
	svn revision 412

